snippet: Jonas Blixt shot a three-under-par 67 and finished at 13 under to win by two strokes, his second PGA Tour victory.
abstract: Jonas Blixt wins rain-delayed Greenbrier Classic in White Sulphur Springs, W Va; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jonas Blixt shot a three-under-par 67 and finished at 13 under to win by two strokes, his second PGA Tour victory.

headline.main: Swede Overcomes Four-Shot Deficit to Win Greenbrier Classic
